info.description:
Run the Tests
-------------

Install tox and run it::

    pip install tox
    tox

Limit the tests to a specific python version::

    tox -e py27

Conventions
-----------

Onegov Feriennet follows PEP8 as close as possible. To test for it run::

    tox -e pep8

Onegov Feriennet uses `Semantic Versioning <http://semver.org/>`_

info.name: onegov.feriennet
info.html_description:
Run the Tests

Install tox and run it:

pip install tox
tox

Limit the tests to a specific python version:

tox -e py27

Conventions

Onegov Feriennet follows PEP8 as close as possible. To test for it run:

tox -e pep8

Onegov Feriennet uses Semantic Versioning

Build Status

Coverage

Latest PyPI Release

License

onegov.feriennet is released under GPLv2
